              "On your route, you will pass by the Genesis GlamBot station. You are positioned on the far side of it — you do not need to engage with it or offer it to guests. Just keep moving to the Portrait Lounge.",
              "Smart Water is available at the end of the carpet but will be too far out of your path — you do not need to offer it",
              "All guests have received advance communications letting them know they've been selected for a specialty content opportunity with Gold House.",
              "",
              "If a guest does not want to participate, there is no pressure whatsoever"
